post.description:
This call completes the registration.  Once the registration is submitted, it is processed asynchronously.  The status can be checked using
the [get cart status](#getCartStatus) api call.  However, the [Get Receipt](#getCartReceipt) call is immediately available.

Example request body:

```json
{
  "version": "AAAAAAmirMM=",
  "customer": {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.org"
  },
  "payment_info": [
    {
      "payment_method_amount": 90,
      "apply_system_credit_amount": 10,
      "billing_method": {
        "id": "PTLvg3hhYLPUqaBJcHIybjIokxLwR6RHG4zdhF6zZQdZM",
        "save": true
      },
      "line_item_payments": [
        {
          "line_item_id": "4f04bd57-a51b-4d55-85ea-b6f4d7a64090",
          "amount": 40,
          "schedule_remaining": false
        },
        {
          "line_item_id": "fe591b03-79a6-4d07-a0ac-64574a35896d",
          "amount": 60,
          "schedule_remaining": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
